title: Jaineck Chinyanta
text: Jaineck Chinyanta (born 1 August 1958) is a Zambian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201984%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Lightweight">men's lightweight</a> event at the <a href="1984%20Summer%20Olympics">1984 Summer Olympics</a>.
